  "title": "Sales Exectuive",
  "description": "<h2>Sales Executive </h2><h3>Job Description</h3><p>We are looking for a dynamic and result-oriented <strong>Sales Executive</strong> to join our Tours & Travels team. The ideal candidate will be responsible for promoting travel packages, handling customer enquiries, closing sales, and building long-term client relationships.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Promote and sell tour packages (local & international) to walk-in customers, corporate clients, and online enquiries</p></li><li><p>Understand customer travel requirements and recommend suitable packages</p></li><li><p>Handle enquiries via phone, email, WhatsApp, and social media platforms</p></li><li><p>Prepare quotations, follow up with clients, and close sales effectively</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with operations team for bookings, documentation, and travel arrangements</p></li><li><p>Achieve monthly and annual sales targets</p></li><li><p>Maintain accurate customer records and sales reports</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain strong relationships with clients and travel partners</p></li><li><p>Provide after-sales support to ensure customer satisfaction</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>1–3 years of experience</strong> in sales (experience in tours & travels is an added advantage)</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Customer-focused with a positive attitude</p></li><li><p>Ability to work under pressure and meet sales targets</p></li><li><p>Basic knowledge of travel destinations, visas, hotels, and flight bookings is preferred</p></li><li><p>Proficient in MS Office and basic CRM systems</p></li><li><p>Willingness to work weekends or holidays if required</p></li></ul><h3>Qualifications</h3><ul><li><p>Diploma or Bachelor’s degree in Travel & Tourism, Business, or a related field (preferred)</p></li></ul><h3>Salary & Benefits</h3><ul><li><p>Attractive basic salary + commission</p></li><li><p>Incentives based on performance</p></li><li><p>Opportunities for career growth</p></li><li><p>Training provided</p></li></ul><p></p>",
