    "description": "<p>Registration No. / Unique Entity Number: 201710306R issued by Accounting And Corporate Regulatory Authority<br>\nNISSI TOURS AND TRAVELS PTE. LTD. (the \"Company\") is a Exempt Private Company Limited by Shares, incorporated on 12 April 2017 (Wednesday) in Singapore . The address of the Company's registered office is 102 RANGOON ROAD, #01-01, SINGAPORE (218385). The Company current operating status is live and has been operating for 8 years. This Company's principal activity is travel agencies and tour operators (mainly inbound) with online marketplaces for travel services as the secondary activity.</p>",
